></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250814/1032672361796734976301465.png/Wex3mAJfODlqAmsnGtZ6sxoQlqbGZ2Ar-j7o0vo-6NI\" alt=\"吹牛吹到殺死人？1999年水泥罐燒殺事件始末揭盅　因虛榮心釀悲劇（Unsplash＠lausteff）\"><figcaption>吹牛吹到殺死人？1999年水泥罐燒殺事件始末揭盅　因虛榮心釀悲劇（Unsplash＠lausteff）</figcaption></figure><p>【本文獲「Japaholic」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-04T15:29:03.626601+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":3101,"images":39,"source":"HK01 熱話","fallback":"none"}}